## **5\. Appendix**

### **5.1 Sample Questions for chatbot**

The task during build up a Virtual Commissioning (VC) is, to position all kinds of conveyor, turn tables and so on in a 3D software. Moreover, each material handling component contains one or more tracks. The VC engineer has to connect the tracks of neighboring components. Hence possible questions might include

* What is the general layout of the plant?   
  * a production plant is normally divided into Enterprise/Resource/Site/Area/ProductionLine/Cell  
  * also the VC can have different focus (e.g. only cell level)  
* Which material handling components are installed in ST101?  
  * this would return all components of the specific cell  
* What conveyors are connected upstream and downstream of conveyor C?  
  * this helps to connect the tracks  
* What is the complete material flow path from A to B?  
  * an other question that helps to connect the tracks  
* Where is C positioned?  
  * this helps to position the elements in the 3D software  
  * positions in the data might be absolute or relative to a frame
